column1: Levi’s Wedgie High-Waisted Jean – Shut Up
column2: Levi’s high-rise wedgie jean for a vintage look we love. In a classic rigid denim with straight-leg fit that’s slightly slouchy through the thigh and tapers in at the ankle. Features a frayed, raw-edge hem and 5-pocket design.

column1: FILA Disruptor 2 Premium Mono Sneaker
column2: Perfectly retro-inspired sneakers from the sporty pros at FILA. Evoking sporty-cool vibes with a chunky lace-up silhouette in a sleek, durable leather with branded detailing at sides + heel. Finished with a chunky, lugged rubber sole for major cushioning and a no-slip grip.

column1: Champion Reverse Weave Fleece Crew Neck Sweatshirt
column2: Essential pullover sweatshirt from Champion. Ultra-soft cotton fleece with a cozy brushed interior is cut in a standard fit with rib-knit banding at the crew neck, cuffs, side panels + hem. Finished with embroidered C logo patches at the chest and left sleeve. Champion has been offering its innovative athletic apparel for men and women since 1919.

column1: FILA UO Exclusive Full-Zip Cozy Sherpa Hoodie Jacket
column2: Ultra-plush zip-up sherpa sweatshirt from FILA, available exclusively from UO. Ultra-warm poly is cut in a standard fit, complete with zip-front closure and adjustable drawstring hood. Finished with zipped pocket at chest and embroidered logo detailing.

column1: Champion Reverse Weave Jogger Pant
column2: Essential joggers in colors we love from Champion. Ultra-plush reverse weave fleece is cut in an athletic fit offering rib-knit banding at the hem and an elastic waist with an inner adjustable drawstring. Finished with side seam pockets, single back patch pocket and a mini embroidered C logo patch on the left thigh. Champion has been offering its innovative athletic apparel for men and women since 1919.

column1: Champion UO Exclusive Reverse Weave Hoodie Sweatshirt
column2: Your favorite Champion hoodie, now available in colors we love that are only at Urban Outfitters! Classic pullover silhouette in a durable reverse weave cotton fleece features a soft brushed interior to keep you cozy. Cut with a slightly dropped shoulder for a slouchy look and rib-knit banding at the cuffs + hem for a comfortable fit. column1: Vagabond Shoemakers Olivia Suede Boot
column2: Step with chic confidence in this heeled ankle boot by Vagabond Shoemakers. Cut above the ankle in a soft suede with a pointed toe + invisible zipper entry at inner ankle. Finished with a sculpted covered bell heel + a rubber sole.
